data.description: CHARMING 2 STORY HOME IN NORTHWEST ALBANY! CORNER LOT! FOAM INSULATED! Wonderful location and neighborhood that is so convenient to everything yet in a quiet and mature area! This 3-bedroom 2 bath all brick home features 1790 sqft, all brick exterior and sits on .41 of an acre! Spacious living room complete with laminate hardwood floors and fireplace! Open kitchen complete with updated tile floors, pantry, loads of updated counter and cabinet space, backsplash, breakfast bar and dining area! A bedroom and full updated bathroom are on the first floor! Upstairs boasts two massive bedrooms with ample closet space and a full updated bathroom! Outside has a fenced in yard, gutters, super screened in porch, HVAC 6 years old, new vapor barrier and foam insulation in the attic! This is a great value for the area!
